Transform your browser workflow
Give your browser superpowers and handle tabs and bookmarks with greater ease using Zeistab's intuitive interface.


Organize your tabs in groups. Select multiple ones and move them around.
Move tab groups around and change their name and color.

Features include:

✔︎ Manage tabs
✔︎ Manage tab groups
✔︎ Find the current tab playing music and mute/unmute it
✔︎ Import bookmarks and top sites
✔︎ Organize bookmarks
✔︎ Search sites and items

Try without an account. No need to pay.

Questions or requests? We are always open to feedback.
